@startuml
title Indoor Map with Heatmap - Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "ViewController" as VC
participant "FloorplanOverlay" as FO
participant "FloorplanOverlayRenderer" as FOR
participant "CoordinateConverter" as CC
participant "VisibleMapRegionDelegate" as VMRD
participant "MapKit" as MK
participant "Backend API\n(Node.js/Express)" as API
participant "MongoDB" as DB
participant "CustomPolygons" as CP

== Application Initialization ==
User -> VC: Launch Application
activate VC
VC -> MK: Initialize MKMapView
activate MK
VC -> VMRD: Set as map delegate
activate VMRD
VC -> API: GET /floorplan.pdf
activate API
API -> DB: Query map data
activate DB
DB --> API: Return map data
deactivate DB
API -> API: Generate PDF floorplan
API --> VC: Return PDF floorplan
deactivate API
VC -> FO: Create FloorplanOverlay(pdf)
activate FO
FO -> FO: Load PDF document
FO -> CC: Initialize coordinate conversion
activate CC
CC -> CC: Setup GeoAnchor pairs
CC --> FO: Conversion ready
deactivate CC
FO --> VC: Overlay created
deactivate FO
VC -> MK: Add overlay to map
MK -> FOR: Create renderer for overlay
activate FOR
FOR --> MK: Renderer ready
deactivate FOR
MK --> VC: Map initialized
deactivate MK
deactivate VC

== Fetch and Display Heatmap Data ==
User -> VC: View map
activate VC
VC -> API: GET /trigger-events
activate API
API -> DB: Query trigger events
activate DB
DB --> API: Return event data
deactivate DB
API --> VC: Return trigger events
deactivate API
VC -> VC: Process event data
VC -> CP: Create heatmap polygons/circles
activate CP
CP --> VC: Return overlays
deactivate CP
VC -> MK: Add heatmap overlays
activate MK
MK -> FOR: Render overlays
activate FOR
FOR -> FO: Get PDF coordinate bounds
activate FO
FO -> CC: Convert coordinates
activate CC
CC --> FO: Return geographic coords
deactivate CC
FO --> FOR: Return bounds
deactivate FO
FOR -> FOR: Draw PDF floorplan
FOR -> FOR: Draw heatmap overlay
FOR --> MK: Rendering complete
deactivate FOR
MK --> VC: Display updated
deactivate MK
deactivate VC

== User Interaction - Map Navigation ==
User -> VC: Pan/Zoom map
activate VC
VC -> VMRD: Map region changed
activate VMRD
VMRD -> FO: Get floorplan bounds
activate FO
FO --> VMRD: Return bounds
deactivate FO
VMRD -> VMRD: Check if within bounds
alt Outside bounds
    VMRD -> MK: Restrict camera position
    activate MK
    MK --> VMRD: Camera adjusted
    deactivate MK
else Within bounds
    VMRD -> MK: Allow movement
    activate MK
    MK --> VMRD: Movement allowed
    deactivate MK
end
VMRD --> VC: Region update handled
deactivate VMRD
deactivate VC

== Trigger Event (User Generated) ==
User -> VC: Trigger event at location
activate VC
VC -> VC: Get current location
VC -> API: POST /trigger-events\n(location, timestamp)
activate API
API -> DB: Insert trigger event
activate DB
DB --> API: Event stored
deactivate DB
API --> VC: Event created
deactivate API
VC -> VC: Refresh heatmap data
VC -> API: GET /trigger-events
activate API
API -> DB: Query updated events
activate DB
DB --> API: Return events
deactivate DB
API --> VC: Return updated events
deactivate API
VC -> CP: Update heatmap overlays
activate CP
CP --> VC: Updated overlays
deactivate CP
VC -> MK: Refresh map overlays
activate MK
MK -> FOR: Re-render
activate FOR
FOR --> MK: Rendering complete
deactivate FOR
MK --> VC: Display updated
deactivate MK
deactivate VC

== Backend Data Management ==
participant "random.js\n(Simulator)" as SIM
SIM -> API: POST /trigger-events\n(simulated data)
activate API
API -> DB: Insert simulated events
activate DB
DB --> API: Events stored
deactivate DB
API --> SIM: Events created
deactivate API

== Coordinate Conversion ==
VC -> CC: Convert PDF to Geographic
activate CC
CC -> CC: Apply transformation\nusing GeoAnchor pairs
CC --> VC: Return lat/long coordinates
deactivate CC

@enduml
